{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"462959a0f6","title":"围攻三边地区土厘要有周详的计划","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7905a1af7f","index":0,"year":1937,"month":11,"day":28,"articleId":"462959a0f6"}],"tags":[{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji11","name":"毛泽东全集第11卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji11.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji11":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3e5e44864b","type":"paragraph","text":"围攻三边地区土厘要有周详的计划","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"462959a0f6"},{"id":"fba8493c4c","type":"paragraph","text":"1937年11月28日）高岗同志（一）张范两据守土围，强攻土围须有产密的侦察，周详的计划，并对围内及围外之敌须有严密的警戒，不可疏忽（二）即请将士围巩固状况，之兵力工事，设备粮草柴水之供给，群众条件及证外援之可能性详细查明告我（三）二十七军是否有追击炮，攻坚的火力如何，均请告，在未有十分把握以前不可轻动","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"462959a0f6"},{"id":"3e5c80b406","type":"paragraph","text":"毛萧","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"462959a0f6"},{"id":"f954ce204b","type":"paragraph","text":"二十八日十五时[1]这是毛泽东和中共中央军委参谋长、八路军后方总留守处主任萧劲光给八路军陕甘宁边区保安司令部司令员高岗的电报。2张范两医，指盘脂在三边（即陕西北部的定边、安边和精边）地区","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"462959a0f6"}],"page":{"id":"be2c4435f1","publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"462959a0f6","start":404,"end":404}}}},"__N_SSG":true}